name: Winter Style
description:
This is a DreamArtist Textual Inversion Style Embedding trained on images of a snowy winter forest/cabin scene. You can get amazing winter colors and snow effects in your images by calling Style-Winter in the positive prompt, and if you want to temper the effect, also call Style-Winter-neg in the negative prompt.

Note: SD 2.x version here!

If you'd like the effect to come through stronger (some models need it), try bumping up the emphasis on Style-Winter - see the prompts in the images below.

Please consider joining my Patreon! Advanced SD tutorials, settings explanations, adult-art, from a female content creator (me!) patreon.com/theally

Props to Elldreth for the many hours spent figuring this all out with me! Go check his models.
